These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: ebony, azure
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, german
City: liverpool, new-york
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, skateboard
1. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the german##8
2. the german is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
3. the person who likes ebony is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Color      | azure     | ebony      |
| Nationality          | german | turkish    |
| City         | new-york   | liverpool |
| Transport   | subway  | skateboard      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different pets are kept: ferret, cat
2 different games are played: snooker, chess
City: edinburgh, rome
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, zombie
1. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
2. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
3. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
4. the person watching time-travel movies is not the person playing chess##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Pet    | ferret        | cat    |
| Game       | snooker         | chess |
| City         | rome | edinburgh   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel               | zombie  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, january
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, cycling
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, blue
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, boat
1. the person who likes turquise is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes blue is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Birthday   | november       | january |
| Sport   | rowing       | cycling    |
| Color   | turquise | blue |
| Transport           | ship        | boat   |

