.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, july
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, lacrosse
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, turquise
There 2 different types of food: radish, avocado
1. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
2. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
3. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Birthday         | july | february  |
| Sport           | lacrosse  | parkour |
| Color   | turquise | grey   |
| Food     | avocado   | radish |

