.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-5::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, bellflower
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
2 different pets are kept: snake, goat
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, game
1. the game-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Flower   | dahlia | bellflower |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | 7up     |
| Pet         | snake  | goat    |
| Cigar     | game     | siglo       |

