3. the fan of folk is not to the right of the colombian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |
| Nationality        | mexican             | colombian     |
| Color         | orange | green  |
| Hobby         | sudoku           | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | electronic              | folk |

