The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, basketball
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bolivar
House: townhouse, victorian
1. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
2. the townhouse house is the townhouse house##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the davidoff-smoker##5
4. the townhouse house is not to the right of the victorian house##8
5. the victorian house is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
