.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-20::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, light-blue
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit
1. the person who growsorchid is not to the right of the person who likes light-blue##8
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Color          | light-blue         | fuchsia    |
| Beverage           | coffee | sprite   |
| Flower   | orchid   | poppy    |
| Pet     | hedgehog         | rabbit |

 